Mauritius Health Minister Hanoomanjee Arrested, Graft Agency’s Ram Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y   a n d   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-07-22T08:32:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/mauritius-health-minister-hanoomanjee-arrested-graft-agency-s-ram-says.html
Mauritian Health Minister Santi Bai
Hanoomanjee was arrested under provisional charges of favoritism
in awarding a tender for a hospital, according to court
documents.  Hanoomanjee “ensured that all measures were taken and
directives given for MedPoint Ltd. to be favored over other
bidders,” according to the charge sheet filed in court in  Port
Louis , the capital, today.  She was arrested by the  Independent Commission Against
Corruption , the agency’s spokesman Suresh Ram said. Hanoomanjee
was released on bail, according to court documents.  To contact the reporters on this story:
